    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It exhibits noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior. Some mechanical components are nearing the end of their service life and will require maintenance or repair in the near future. The car is currently operational.",
